<i>noun</i>: 계피 [계ː피/게ː피] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>계피 [계ː피/게ː피]</dt><br>
<dd>cinnamon</dd><br>
<dd>향료나 한약재로 쓰며, 매운 향이 나고 붉은 갈색인 계수나무의 속껍질.</dd><br>
<dd>A spicy, reddish-brown inner bark of trees from the genus Cinnamomum used in oriental herbal medicine or as a seasoning in food.</dd><br>
